Getopt-ApacheCommonsCLI version 0.01
======================================

SYNOPSIS

Getopt::ApacheCommonsCLI implements the Apache Commons CLI Java options parsing library in Perl
by calling Getopt::Long first, then post-processing @ARGV.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Getopt::Long

